docs: complete README overhaul for v1.6

Rewritten from scratch to announce all v1.6 features:
- Predictive analytics engine (VaR, CVaR, time series, Monte Carlo)
- Adaptive speculative decoding (dynamic exit threshold 2-8)
- Adaptive per-layer k (10-pass calibration, per-layer sparsity)
- Harder sparsity targets (k=3.0, max_spike=15)
- QAT for both 4B and 9B models (LoRA rank 128)
- Linux x86_64 + AMD ROCm platform focus
- New analytics API endpoints documented
- Updated technical specs, project structure, roadmap
